						               													<description>EVERYTHING DIES&amp;hellip;EVEN MACHINES&amp;#10;&amp;#10;We have watched the Saints of the Forsaken march across thewastes to do battle for the ruling Prevailers. The Outcasts have scavenged a living in the corners of the frontier. We have reeled in terror at the cannibal rituals of the horrific Skarrd tribes.The savage honor of the Dragyri warrior castes have dragged gasps of awe from each of us. We have even locked our doors at night against the inscrutable monsters of the Brood. The world is soaked in blood and littered with the remains of those who could not weather an existence here. It is a hard life filled withpain, suffering and barbarism&amp;hellip;&amp;hellip;and it just got a whole lot worse. Within this book you will find a new evolution to Dark Age. This includes the Cult of Metamorphosis, a new tribal faction within the Skarrd created from the fully transformed cabal of the Heretic Saint Johann, and the C.O.R.E. &amp;ndash; a never before seen army of tireless robots on a murderous rampage of expansion. Samaria&amp;hellip;and Dark Age&amp;hellip;will never be the same again.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
